  "siteName": "月之暗面 Kimi",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:center;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100000539\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5453703703703704\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2160\" style=\"width: 784px;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmecoa.qpic.cn/sz_mmecoa_png/Cemp46bhCiaxZrlHoCLBkl40q5QXHdkuaGvIJuk4RH2WH7ZbgujkW3iaL7Br1HteaRic1dSGbiat8JxGUJQ26DUXgw/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"245\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"315\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1aca374e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmecoa.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmecoa_png%2FCemp46bhCiaxZrlHoCLBkl40q5QXHdkuaGvIJuk4RH2WH7ZbgujkW3iaL7Br1HteaRic1dSGbiat8JxGUJQ26DUXgw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:justify;\"><span data-eleid=\"8\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在金融投资领域，信息处理的深度与速度直接决定了决策质量。</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:justify;\"><span data-eleid=\"8\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">对于一名资深分析师而言，复盘一家大型企业的海外并购史，往往意味着要查阅跨越十年的财报、公告及研报，并手动拆解复杂的资产负债表变化。如今，依托能力越来越强的专业投研 Agent 产品，这些高强度的基础投研工作正被 AI 重塑。</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:left;\"><span data-eleid=\"8\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">FinGPT Agent 是一款搭载于熵简科技旗下 AlphaEngine 平台(</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://www.alphaengine.top/\" textvalue=\"www.alphaengine.top\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">www.alphaengine.top</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">)的智能投研助手，该平台目前每月服务 7000 余家资管机构，6 到 7 万名基金经理、投资经理及分析师。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">为了应对投研场景下，对长程任务工具调用可靠性的高要求，FinGPT Agent 近期完成了主力模型的更迭，升级为 Kimi K2 Thinking，并降低了 60% 的业务成本。</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:center;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100000543\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6296875\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width: 784px;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"364\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4a1da66e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmecoa.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmecoa_png%2FCemp46bhCiaxZrlHoCLBkl40q5QXHdkua5qbFcqfSghwVpejJZyYcuCkdR2icibu5FRuwAS4bCPagRMuDFuvk3ygg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:justify;\"><span data-eleid=\"8\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: bold;\">复杂投研场景下的「工具调用」挑战</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:justify;\"><span data-eleid=\"22\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">金融投研任务的本质并非简单的对话，而是涉及多个步骤的复杂执行链条。</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:justify;\"><span data-eleid=\"22\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一个典型的投研指令，如「分析紫金矿业过去数次海外并购对资产负债表的影响」，需要 Agent 完成任务拆解、研报查询、财务数据提取、逻辑对比以及报告撰写等一系列环节。在这种高要求场景中，Agent 往往需要执行多达数百步的工具调用和思考过程。</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:center;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100000544\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.66953125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width: 784px;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"387\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d9d92fea&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmecoa.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmecoa_png%2FCemp46bhCiaxZrlHoCLBkl40q5QXHdkuaDXXLtTobK2SdibuxaZEfLxMajuVTaltzJW75YO2C2XCegFHWwUTicMDA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:justify;\"><span data-eleid=\"22\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">在多轮严格的内部实测中，熵简科技发现，Kimi K2 Thinking 是目前唯一能够稳定满足此类高难度、复杂需求的国产模型</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">：</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;list-style-type:disc;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">长链条思考稳定性：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Kimi K2 Thinking 能够自主实现多达 300 步的工具调用，且在多步思考过程中保持逻辑的一致性。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">多工具协作：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">FinGPT Agent 目前已接入 22 个投研类工具（包含财务分析、研报查询、估值建模等），Kimi K2 能够更准确地识别任务需求并主动调用相应工具。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">复杂指令理解：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">面对包含多个限制条件的投研指令，Kimi K2 能够以更高的准确度拆解并编排任务顺序。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:justify;\"><span data-eleid=\"22\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span data-eleid=\"8\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: bold;\">独有数据库与 AI Agent 的深度结合</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:justify;\"><span data-eleid=\"22\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">FinGPT Agent 的优势不仅在于熵简对 AI 投研场景丰富的实战经验，还在于它接入了熵简科技多年沉淀的投研资料库。</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:justify;\"><span data-eleid=\"22\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">与仅能获取互联网公开信息的通用 AI 不同，FinGPT Agent 结合了 AlphaEngine 平台的海量深度资讯。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">这意味着 Agent 在执行任务时，不仅是在「检索网页」，更是在调动一整套买方级投研资产</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">：</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;list-style-type:disc;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">全覆盖的会议纪要：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">包含国内外宏观行业、A/H/美上市公司的实时会议记录，音频转写与结构化纪要，支持回溯与深度分析。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">海量外资研报：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">每日更新超过 4000 篇全球维度的专业研报，覆盖国际投行与主流研究机构，支持全文翻译、跨文档检索与问答分析。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">专家访谈数据库：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">拥有海量的专家纪要库，提供一手情报支持，用于补充财务数据之外的产业与趋势判断。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:justify;\"><span data-eleid=\"22\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">通过 Kimi K2 Thinking 对这些非公开、高价值资料的深度学习与逻辑抽取，FinGPT Agent 能够在极短时间内输出极具专业价值的研究成果。</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:justify;\"><span data-eleid=\"22\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: bold;\">实战场景：从海量资料到核心结论</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:justify;\"><span data-eleid=\"22\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在接入 Kimi K2 Thinking 模型 API 后，FinGPT Agent 展现了扎实的长程投研任务执行能力：</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:justify;\"><span data-eleid=\"22\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">宏观政策范式分析识别：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在通胀未完全回落、就业边际走弱的复杂宏观环境下，FinGPT Agent 系统性阅读 252 篇宏观、政策与投行研究报告，并生成 52 篇结构化研究笔记，据此识别美联储政策范式由「抗通胀」向「稳就业」切换的关键拐点，并进一步推演降息路径、资产定价逻辑及跨市场配置影响。</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;margin-bottom:0px;widows:auto;text-align:start;\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10px;\">宏观识别：2026年联储降息推演</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:justify;\"><span data-eleid=\"22\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">产业拐点研究与价值链重构：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">全固态电池迈入工程化临界点在分析固态电池从「半固态商业化」迈向「全固态工程化」的产业跨越时，FinGPT Agent 可系统性拆解硫化物路线的技术主线与量产约束（材料成本、干燥环境、良率爬坡、设备投资强度），并基于多源产业与政策资料生成结构化研究笔记，用于锚定 2025-2027 中试扩产节奏、2027 千辆级装车验证节点及“设备先行、材料突破”的核心受益环节。</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;margin-bottom:0px;widows:auto;text-align:start;\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;padding:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:1.5px;clear:both;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10px;\">产业拐点：全固态电池工程化临界点解析</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:justify;\"><span data-eleid=\"22\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">业务解构与增长引擎研究：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在拆解英伟达「GPU厂商→全球AI计算平台公司」的战略跃迁时，FinGPT Agent 会围绕收入结构（数据中心占比跃升）、软硬一体护城河（GPU+CUDA+NVLink）、产品交付形态（板卡→机架级系统）三条主线进行定量复盘，并进一步延展到产业链约束与竞争格局推演，输出可直接用于买方投研的结构化结论与要点笔记。</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;margin-bottom:0px;widows:auto;text-align:start;\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:center;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10px;\">公司解构：英伟达</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10px;\">的AI平台化跃迁全拆解</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:justify;\"><span data-eleid=\"22\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">完整 Prompt：</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:center;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100000547\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8240109140518418\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1466\" style=\"width: 784px;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmecoa.qpic.cn/sz_mmecoa_png/Cemp46bhCiaxZrlHoCLBkl40q5QXHdkuaypB4eRhZzwSRnxmIVvUI8Cwia34XUIx85efbvXpkJfV7fzgKhlnWYYw/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"482\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"476\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d780f5f6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmecoa.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmecoa_png%2FCemp46bhCiaxZrlHoCLBkl40q5QXHdkuaypB4eRhZzwSRnxmIVvUI8Cwia34XUIx85efbvXpkJfV7fzgKhlnWYYw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:justify;\"><span data-eleid=\"22\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span data-eleid=\"8\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 24px 8px;text-align: justify;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-eleid&quot;:&quot;8&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: bold;\">持续突破投研效率边界</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:justify;\"><span data-eleid=\"22\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">在投研 Agent 这一「知识密集」的皇冠领域，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">Kimi K2 Thinking 模型经过严格实测成为唯一选项</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">，进一步验证了 Kimi 旗舰模型解决长耗时、多步骤任务时的性能优势。与此同时，熵简科技内部分析显示，将 Agent 主力模型升级为 Kimi K2 Thinking 之后，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">这项业务的 API 成本也降低了 60%</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">， 让原本受限于成本的复杂分析任务得以在日常工作中实现常态化使用。</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:justify;\"><span data-eleid=\"22\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">目前，熵简科技的 AlphaEngine 已累计服务 7000 余家资管机构。搭载于 AlphaEngine 平台的新一代 AI 投研产品 FinGPT Agent，深度融合先进的模型能力与行业专有数据，正将专业投研人员</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">从繁杂的资料收集与初级数据整理中解放出来，使其回归到「挖掘非共识逻辑」的核心工作中</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">。预计随着底层 AI 模型能力的持续提升，能够支持更长时间、更高难度的任务，金融投研的效率边界也将持续获得突破。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"> \n      <br> \n     </span></span></span></p>\n  <hr style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0px 0px;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);transform-origin: 0px 0px;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:left;\"><span data-eleid=\"22\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">快速访问</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;list-style-type:square;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span data-eleid=\"22\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">熵简科技 AlphaEngine：</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://www.alphaengine.top/\" textvalue=\"www.alphaengine.top\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">www.alphaengine.top</span></a></span></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span data-eleid=\"22\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Kimi API 开放平台：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://platform.moonshot.cn/\" textvalue=\"platform.moonshot.cn\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">platform.moonshot.cn</span></a></span></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:center;\"><span data-eleid=\"24\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 24px 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0px 8px 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-eleid&quot;:&quot;24&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">- 他们都在用 Kimi K2 -</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <hr style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0px 0px;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);transform-origin: 0px 0px;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:center;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100000489\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.34375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width: 784px;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmecoa.qpic.cn/sz_mmecoa_jpg/Cemp46bhCiaxplRCCjqgXjJiaEzHljL69cZjW1F4IM1Nk6FIwgN7caL1icjCgEPRvlibmx4yZ3FFiaKxjldmbicJADYA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"325\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"777\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9273cd36&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmecoa.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmecoa_jpg%2FCemp46bhCiaxplRCCjqgXjJiaEzHljL69cZjW1F4IM1Nk6FIwgN7caL1icjCgEPRvlibmx4yZ3FFiaKxjldmbicJADYA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:start;\">\n   <br>\n  </p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "熵简科技的 FinGPT Agent 升级 Kimi K2 Thinking 模型，显著提升了金融投研中复杂任务的执行稳定性、工具调用能力和成本效益，并结合独有数据库，将 AI 应用于金融投研领域，大幅提高效率。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "熵简科技的 FinGPT Agent 升级 Kimi K2 Thinking 模型，显著提升了金融投研中复杂任务的执行稳定性、工具调用能力和成本效益，并结合独有数据库，将 AI 应用于金融投研领域，大幅提高效率。",
  "summary": "文章介绍了熵简科技旗下的智能投研助手 FinGPT Agent 如何升级其主力模型至 Kimi K2 Thinking，以应对金融投研领域复杂且高强度的信息处理需求。FinGPT Agent 每月服务数万名金融投研人员，其面临的关键挑战在于复杂投研场景下的工具调用稳定性、多工具协作能力和复杂指令理解。文章强调 Kimi K2 Thinking 模型在长链条思考稳定性（300 步工具调用）、多工具（22 个投研工具）协作和复杂指令理解方面的优异表现，是目前唯一能稳定满足需求且能降低 60%业务成本的国产模型。此外，FinGPT Agent 结合了熵简科技多年沉淀的非公开、高价值投研数据库，使其具备了超越通用 AI 的深度分析能力。文章通过宏观政策范式分析、产业拐点研究和公司解构等实战案例，展示了 FinGPT Agent 在新模型加持下，从海量资料中快速抽取核心结论，显著提升投研效率的优势。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "金融投研领域对 AI Agent 的需求在于处理复杂、长链条任务和多源数据。",
      "explanation": "金融投研工作涉及大量资料查阅、数据分析和报告撰写，需要 AI Agent 具备稳定执行多步骤工具调用、协作多种投研工具，并理解复杂指令的能力，以提升效率和决策质量。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Kimi K2 Thinking 模型在复杂投研场景下展现了卓越的稳定性与性能。",
      "explanation": "Kimi K2 Thinking 能够自主实现数百步工具调用并保持逻辑一致性，准确识别任务需求并调用相关工具，同时能以高准确度拆解复杂指令，有效应对金融投研的高难度需求。"
    },
